		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Digital means that the sound playback is from sequenced samples, and anolog means that the sound playback from a basic waveform, not from sequenced data at all. Instead of talking about analog/digital sound, talking about anaglog/digital sound source would be a bit more correct.

		

		</td>
